  "text": "On the whole slide overview of the image section, ROIs were drawn manually using the zooming and mark-up tools included in the StrataQuest 5.0 software, part of TissueFAXS plus solution. The need to analyze and compare different regions within the tumor tissue was derived from the observation that the proliferation compartment [CITATION_1] as well as the expression of proteins like -catenin and cyclin D1 [CITATION_2] was not equally distributed in the tumor mass. Heterogeneities in the structures were also seen in noncancerous parts of the mucosa in CRC samples [CITATION_3] .",
